{"word":"σίττᾰ","slug":"σίττᾰ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n94440\" key=\"si/ttă\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σίττᾰ</orth>, a cry of drovers to urge on or guide their flocks (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>), <sense id=\"n94440.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">st!</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σίττα, νέμεσθε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:69\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.69</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σίτθ᾽, ὁ λέπαργος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.45</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; when <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπό</foreign> follows, to drive them off, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐκ ἀπὸ τᾶς κράνας σίττ᾽, ἀμνίδες</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.3</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σίττ᾽ ἀπὸ τᾶς κοτίνω</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:100\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">100</biblScope> </bibl>; when <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πρός</foreign> follows, to lead them on, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σίτθ᾽, ἁ Κυμαίθα, ποτὶ τὸν λόφον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:46\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.46</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψίττα, ψύττα</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}